outputs.output_descr: TOKTEN, along with other CD interventions, has been alligned with support to the implementation of PRS which was from July 2008 to June 2011- end date now extended to Dec 2011.

project_descr: The project seeks to build Capacity of Government of Liberia (GOL) ministries and agencies to carry out by their assigned functions as per their mandates by attracting competent professionals from the Diaspora
